---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="FAQ | Free Resume Builder" description="Frequently asked questions about our free online resume builder. Learn how to create, customize, and export your professional resume.">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.25rem">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2.5rem">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.25rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:0.75rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--gray-500);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto">Everything you need to know about using our free resume builder.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem">
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">Is this resume builder really free?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no credit card required, no limits on how many resumes you create. All templates and features are available at no cost.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">Do I need to create an account?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">No account or sign-up is required. Your resume data is stored locally in your browser, so you can start building immediately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">Can I download my resume as a PDF?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">Yes, you can export your resume as a PDF with one click. The PDF preserves your formatting and is ready to submit to employers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">Are your templates ATS-friendly?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">Yes, all our templates are designed to be parsed correctly by Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS). We avoid complex layouts that can confuse automated screeners.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">How many templates do you offer?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">We currently offer four professional templates: Classic, Modern, Professional, and Creative. Each can be customized with 7 different color themes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">Is my data safe?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">Your resume data stays on your device. We don't store or transmit your personal information to any servers. Your privacy is our priority.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">Can I use the resume builder on my phone?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">Yes, the resume builder is fully responsive and works on smartphones, tablets, and desktop browsers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">What if I lose my resume data?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">We recommend exporting your resume as PDF when you're done. Clearing your browser data will remove locally stored resumes. Your data is stored in your browser's local storage — use the same browser to recover it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">Can I create multiple resumes?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">Yes, you can create as many resumes as you like. Simply clear the form and start fresh, or customize your existing resume for different applications.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:1.25rem">
        <h3 style="font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin:0 0 0.5rem">How do I add my work experience?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.6;margin:0">Navigate to the "Experience" tab in the builder and click "Add Experience". Fill in your job details and add bullet points describing your achievements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="background:var(--gray-50);border-top:1px solid var(--gray-200);border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200);padding:3rem 1.5rem">
    <div style="max-width:960px;margin:0 auto">
      <h3 style="font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:1.25rem;text-align:center">Free Career Tools</h3>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(130px,1fr));gap:0.75rem">
        <a href="/" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Resume Builder</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/ats-score" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">ATS Score</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/cover-letter" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Cover Letter</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Examples</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/templates" class="card card-hover" style="padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;text-align:center">
          <span style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--primary-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gray-700)">Templates</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#1d4ed8);padding:3rem 1.5rem;text-align:center">
    <div style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto">
      <h3 style="font-size:1.375rem;font-weight:800;color:white;margin:0 0 0.5rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Get Weekly Resume Tips</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.9375rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 1.25rem">Join 10,000+ job seekers getting expert advice straight to their inbox.</p>
      <form style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;max-width:400px;margin:0 auto" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();var e=this.querySelector('input');if(e.value){alert('Thanks for subscribing!');e.value=''}">
        <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" style="flex:1;border-radius:8px;border:none;padding:0.625rem 0.875rem;font-size:0.875rem;font-family:inherit;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)" required />
        <button type="submit" style="border-radius:8px;border:none;background:#0f172a;color:white;padding:0.625rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:all 0.15s;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
      <p style="font-size:0.6875rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin:0.625rem 0 0">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Is this resume builder really free?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no credit card required, no limits on how many resumes you create. All templates and features are available at no cost."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Do I need to create an account?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No account or sign-up is required. Your resume data is stored locally in your browser, so you can start building immediately."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Can I download my resume as a PDF?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, you can export your resume as a PDF with one click. The PDF preserves your formatting and is ready to submit to employers."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Are your templates ATS-friendly?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, all our templates are designed to be parsed correctly by Applicant Tracking Systems (ATS). We avoid complex layouts that can confuse automated screeners."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"How many templates do you offer?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"We currently offer four professional templates: Classic, Modern, Professional, and Creative. Each can be customized with different color themes."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Is my data safe?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Your resume data stays on your device. We don't store or transmit your personal information to any servers. Your privacy is our priority."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Can I use the resume builder on my phone?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, the resume builder is fully responsive and works on smartphones, tablets, and desktop browsers."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"What if I lose my resume data?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"We recommend exporting your resume as PDF when you're done. Clearing your browser data will remove locally stored resumes. Your data is stored in your browser's local storage - use the same browser to recover it."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"Can I create multiple resumes?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, you can create as many resumes as you like. Simply clear the form and start fresh, or customize your existing resume for different applications."}},
      {"@type":"Question","name":"How do I add my work experience?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Navigate to the 'Experience' tab in the builder and click 'Add Experience'. Fill in your job details and add bullet points describing your achievements."}}
    ]
  }
  </script>
</Layout>